title: William Bernstein - 6 books (epub)
description:
Great neurologist turned investor, these books will make you a more intelligent stock market investor. Also a great historian, highly recommended!


The Four Pillars of Investing
If You Can..
The Investor's Manifesto
Splendid Exchange: How Trade Shaped the World
The Birth of Plenty
Masters of the Word
